

1. Navigated into the project:
   cd alx-intermediate-frontend

2. Created the new directory:
   mkdir 0x03-sass_scss
   cd 0x03-sass_scss

3. Installed Node.js using NVM:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
   exit (then reopened terminal)
   nvm install 20.16.0
   nvm use 20.16.0

4. Installed Sass using NPM:
   npm install sass@1.37.4
